    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for VAD use with compensating controls: independent experimental replication at two additional operating points, mandatory review of boundary condition setup, and commitment to complete Monte Carlo UQ registration for all validation results in the next assessment cycle. Uncertainty is discussed extensively in the technical report; formal UQ artifact linkage is planned but not yet complete for all validation results.",
